title: wooden theme
description: n the custom wooden theme for the game Narrow One, designed by Pratik, the profile corner has been enhanced to display the player's total kills and deaths. This theme features a rustic, wooden aesthetic that adds a unique touch to the game's interface. To apply this theme, users may need to use a tool like Tamper Monkey for browser customization. The wooden theme provides a warm and natural look, distinguishing it from other themes.
